STATE of North Carolina
v.
Michael A. WILLIAMS. No. 442P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 7, 2006.

Michael A. Williams, Pro Se.

William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC.

AMENDED ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 6th day of June 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 7th day of June 2006."
